Global Ketamine Clinic Market Insights
Ketamine Clinic Market size was valued at USD 1.3 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 4.5 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 20% from 2024 to 2030.

Ketamine Clinic Market Overview
The global ketamine clinic market was valued at USD 2.5 billion in 2024 and is projected to expand at a CAGR of 9.2% from 2024 to 2030. This market growth is primarily driven by the increasing adoption of ketamine as an effective treatment for depression, PTSD, and chronic pain. Ketamine clinics, offering specialized treatments, are gaining popularity as alternatives to traditional mental health therapies. With rising awareness and acceptance of ketamine’s therapeutic potential, especially for individuals who do not respond well to conventional treatments, the market is expected to continue its upward trajectory in the coming years.

